# PROMPT – Orchestrator

Phases:
1) validate_design → `reports/validation_report.md`
2) generate_spec (if not provided) → `reports/spec.md`
3) plan_build → `reports/plan.md`
4) build_screen → code files
5) evaluate_output → `reports/agent_report.md`

Halt on any failed phase; attach diffs and actionable next steps.
